WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.540
Didn't you promise me,

2
00:00:01.680 --> 00:00:02.680
as long as I'm obedient,

3
00:00:02.820 --> 00:00:03.720
you would grant me everything I want?

4
00:00:03.720 --> 00:00:04.460
desires?

5
00:00:04.740 --> 00:00:05.860
I don't really want to let go either.

6
00:00:05.860 --> 00:00:06.740
want to let go.

7
00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:09.040
I only want her to stay by my side,

8
00:00:09.380 --> 00:00:11.140
want my sight to only see her.

9
00:00:11.460 --> 00:00:13.160
To commemorate this, I'll agree to anything.

10
00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:15.560
But, I have a condition.

11
00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:16.240
What?

12
00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:18.240
Kiss me once every day.

13
00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:20.680
Let's start now.

14
00:00:35.860 --> 00:00:37.660
Answer the phone when you want to.

15
00:00:37.740 --> 00:00:39.380
Didn't I tell you?

16
00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:41.760
Don't be nervous around me.

17
00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:45.240
Hello, Mom.

18
00:00:45.480 --> 00:00:46.820
Linlin, you finally turned on your phone.

19
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:48.880
I'm fine, just my phone ran out of battery.

20
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.260
Just now left the store.

21
00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:51.280
It's good that you're okay.

22
00:00:51.420 --> 00:00:52.360
Your dad said you had

23
00:00:52.360 --> 00:00:53.260
something urgent and had to fly back to Rome.

24
00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:54.360
Did something happen?

25
00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:56.300
Nothing, just school suddenly

26
00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:57.160
canceled the holiday.

27
00:00:57.420 --> 00:00:58.280
So I'm going back.

28
00:00:58.780 --> 00:00:59.980
Are you and Dad home already?

29
00:00:59.980 --> 00:01:02.280
Linlin, what's the matter?

30
00:01:02.560 --> 00:01:03.500
What was that sound just now?

